OL,3,CAmy Schumer diagnosis: What is
OL,4,CCushing's syndrome?
OL,6,FWhat is Crushing's syndrome?
OL,8,FCushing's syndrome is a condition
OL,9,Fcaused by having too much of a hormone
OL,10,Fcalled cortisol in your body. It can
OL,11,Fbe serious if it's not treated, .
OL,13,FThe condition is uncommon. It mostly
OL,14,Faffects people who have been taking
OL,15,Fsteroid medicine, especially steroid
OL,16,Ftablets, for a long time.
OL,18,FSteroids contain a synthetic version
OL,19,Fof cortisol. Very rarely, it can be
OL,20,Fcaused by the body producing too much
OL,21,Fcortisol.
