OL,10,FWhen should you seek medical advice?
OL,12,FSee a GP if you have symptoms of
OL,13,FCushing's syndrome, especially if
OL,14,Fyou're taking steroids.
OL,16,FIt is advised that you do not stop
OL,17,Ftaking your medicine without getting
OL,18,Fmedical advice.
