OL,3,CAmy Schumer diagnosis: What is
OL,4,CCushing's syndrome?
OL,6,FLots of things can cause similar
OL,7,Fsymptoms to Cushing's syndrome, so the
OL,8,FNHS recommends getting checked to find
OL,9,Fout what the problem is before acting
OL,10,Fon it.
OL,12,FIs Cushing's syndrome treatable?
OL,14,FAccording to the NHS, Cushing's
OL,15,Fsyndrome usually gets better with
OL,16,Ftreatment, although treatment depends
OL,17,Fon what's causing it.
